data.description: NEW PRICING! Occupy before the holidays! Tasteful updates with over $35k too numerous to list! A few are, updated electrical box, brush nickel plumbing fixtures, double vanities in both baths, quartz c-tops, all new kitchen appliances, sink, custom cabinets with shaker soft close doors, white vinyl solid pane windows, plank flooring with 5' baseboards, 60'x60' beveled mirrors, which all offers an exceptional living experience. Recently installed architectural 30-year roof, painted doors and brick exterior with SW paint and replaced wood facia. Enjoy the tasteful use of  contemporary gray hues that create a soothing ambiance, setting the stage for a life of comfort and style. This one offers an abundance of natural light! Never walk into a dark home again! Whether you enter through the front or back door, you'll be bathed in the gentle glow of under-mount lights in the kitchen that automatically engage and motion lights in both bathrooms & closets. Walk to Walmart and the park!
